                <a href="a3-updates-news-amp-changelogs" class="Permalink" rel="nofollow"><time title="April 16, 2015 10:46PM" datetime="2015-04-16T22:46:24+00:00">April 2015</time></a>            </span>
                <span class="MItem"> <span title="Edited April 21, 2015 10:53PM by PFC Tuomainen." class="DateUpdated">edited April 2015</span> </span>                 <span class="MItem Category"> in <a href="../../categories/public-discussion">Public Discussion</a></span>             </div>
